{"tid":2194611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好掛住你呀...","createTime":"2020-09-08T15:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T17:07:07.000Z","uid":246590,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a53fad68e98a28fe6c374126855063dbec9bc669","tid":2194611,"uid":246590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"我知道我地已經冇可能<br />\n我都以為自己放低左<br />\n但有次無意中偷睇左你IG<br />\n之後就開始心掛掛<br />\n好想知你宜家點<br />\n成日回想如果果時我地可以坦白D, 了解多D,<br />\n唔做咁多錯事, 解開誤會<br />\n大家都肯行前多一步<br />\n就唔會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到後期, 我知我係你心目中已經係可有可無<br />\n你根本唔志在<br />\n甚至分手之後你可能好快已經同條新仔一齊<br />\n<br />\n我知 仲諗緊往事既我好傻<br />\n你地想屌我on9就屌啦<br />\n我已經洗左3次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我想講 我真係好鐘意好鐘意你<br />\n如果所有野可以重新來過就好<br />\n但我都知道已經無可能...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好恨你, 都好愛你"},{"pid":"fbd8ec2d7cd0e9d599c7882a810b08e3bc2997a5","tid":2194611,"uid":347671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a693f6e98dcd2e59bee3a2cca77d3ee68f6630","tid":2194611,"uid":223672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"好想同你重蹈覆轍多一次<br />\n就算結果一樣<br />\n就算一樣都係俾你折磨<br />\n都好想再拖住你<br />\n同你講多一次我愛你"},{"pid":"a962b0b42bb64919666d4b2d7caaf30e511a26d9","tid":2194611,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"一律建議放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dedba72736058ce0b73eb4222c3ccf1f0486557","tid":2194611,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"洗咩洗三次？<br />\n乾淨未？"},{"pid":"6b606e2b3ee958f66ff